\"><sup><span\nstyle='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[948]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>\nîn ..... (<i>adres&#259;</i>), având urm&#259;toarele date de contact<a\nstyle='mso-footnote-id:ftn949' href=\"#_ftn949\" name=\"_ftnref949\" title=\"\"><sup><span\nstyle='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[949]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>\n..... (<i>email, fax, telefon ori altele asemenea</i>),<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n.5in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>în contradictoriu cu pârâtul<a\nstyle='mso-footnote-id:ftn950' href=\"#_ftn950\" name=\"_ftnref950\" title=\"\"><sup><span\nstyle='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sup><span style='font-size:14.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:\nRO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[950]</span></sup></b><![endif]></span></sup></a> </span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>…..<b> </b>(<i>nume, prenume</i>), cu domiciliul în\n..... (<i>adresa</i>), având codul numeric personal ....., <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>sau<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n.5in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>în contradictoriu cu pârâta<a\nstyle='mso-footnote-id:ftn951' href=\"#_ftn951\" name=\"_ftnref951\" title=\"\"><sup><span\nstyle='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sup><span style='font-size:14.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:\nRO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[951]</span></sup></b><![endif]></span></sup></a> </span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>….. (<i>denumirea persoanei juridice</i>), cu\nsediul în ..... (<i>adresa</i>), având num&#259;rul de înmatriculare în\nregistrul comer&#355;ului/num&#259;rul de înscriere în registrul persoanelor\njuridice ….., codul de identificare fiscal&#259; ….. &#351;i contul bancar …..<a\nstyle='mso-footnote-id:ftn952' href=\"#_ftn952\" name=\"_ftnref952\" title=\"\"><sup><span\nstyle='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[952]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>,\nprin reprezentant ….. (<i>nume, prenume</i>), formul&#259;m <b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:center;\nline-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:center;\nline-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>CERERE DE CHEMARE ÎN\nJUDECAT&#258;<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>prin care solicit&#259;m\ninstan&#355;ei:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>1. constatarea\nnulit&#259;&#539;ii absolute/anularea testamentului autentificat sub nr. ….. de\nnotarul public …../testamentului olograf întocmit la data de ….. de defunctul\n…../testamentului privilegiat întocmit în fa&#355;a …../testamentului sumelor\n&#351;i valorilor depozitate întocmit ….. .;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>2. obligarea pârâtului/pârâtei la\nplata cheltuielilor de judecat&#259;<a style='mso-footnote-id:ftn953'\nhref=\"#_ftn953\" name=\"_ftnref953\" title=\"\"><sup><span style='mso-special-character:\nfootnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span style='font-size:14.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:\nRO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[953]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>În fapt</span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>, prin testamentul ……, defunctul ….. a ….. <span\nstyle='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>Testamentul este lovit de\nnulitate absolut&#259;/relativ&#259;, având în vedere c&#259; ….. (<i>se\nindic&#259; cerin&#539;ele de fond sau de form&#259; care au fost\nînc&#259;lcate la întocmirea testamentului</i>).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>Prin urmare, solicit&#259;m\nadmiterea cererii, în sensul celor ar&#259;tate.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>În drept, </span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>ne întemeiem cererea pe dispozi&#355;iile art. –…..</span><a\nstyle='mso-footnote-id:ftn954' href=\"#_ftn954\" name=\"_ftnref954\" title=\"\"><span\nclass=MsoFootnoteReference><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\n\"Times New Roman\",serif'><span style='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><span\nclass=MsoFootnoteReference><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\n115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[954]</span></span><![endif]></span></span></span></a><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'> C. civ.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>În dovedire, </span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>solicit&#259;m încuviin&#355;area probei cu\nînscrisuri, a probei testimoniale, a probei cu interogatoriul pârâtului/pârâtei\n&#351;i a probei cu expertiz&#259; judiciar&#259; în specialitatea ….. .<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>În cadrul probei cu înscrisuri, </span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>depunem urm&#259;toarele înscrisuri<a\nstyle='mso-footnote-id:ftn955' href=\"#_ftn955\" name=\"_ftnref955\" title=\"\"><sup><span\nstyle='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[955]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>:\n....., în copii certificate pentru conformitate cu originalul, în<a\nstyle='mso-footnote-id:ftn956' href=\"#_ftn956\" name=\"_ftnref956\" title=\"\"><sup><span\nstyle='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[956]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a><span\nstyle='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>.....<sup> </sup>exemplare.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>În cadrul probei testimoniale, </span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>indic&#259;m, în vederea audierii în calitate de\nmartor, pe numitul ..... (<i>nume, prenume</i>), cu domiciliul în ..... (<i>adresa</i>),\npentru dovedirea urm&#259;toarelor împrejur&#259;ri de fapt ....., &#351;i\nsolicit&#259;m citarea acestuia.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>În cadrul probei cu interogatoriu</span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>,<b> </b>solicit&#259;m înf&#259;&#355;i&#351;area\nîn persoan&#259; a pârâtului<a style='mso-footnote-id:ftn957' href=\"#_ftn957\"\nname=\"_ftnref957\" title=\"\"><sup><span style='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[957]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>,\nsub sanc&#355;iunea aplic&#259;rii dispozi&#355;iilor art. 358 C. pr. civ.,\npentru dovedirea faptelor personale vizând ...../ata&#351;&#259;m\ninterogatoriul<a style='mso-footnote-id:ftn958' href=\"#_ftn958\"\nname=\"_ftnref958\" title=\"\"><sup><span style='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[958]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>\npentru ca pârâta s&#259; r&#259;spund&#259; în scris, pentru dovedirea faptelor\npersonale vizând ..... .<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:\n35.4pt;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>În cadrul probei cu\nexpertiz&#259; în specialitatea </span></b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;mso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:\nRO'>….., propunem ca expertul s&#259; r&#259;spund&#259; urm&#259;toarelor\nobiective: ....., pentru a dovedi ….. .<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><span style='mso-tab-count:1'>          </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>Solicit&#259;m judecarea cauzei\n&#351;i în lips&#259;<a style='mso-footnote-id:ftn959' href=\"#_ftn959\"\nname=\"_ftnref959\" title=\"\"><sup><span style='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[959]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>,\nîn conformitate cu art. 411 alin. (1) pct. 2 teza final&#259; C. pr. civ.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>Depunem prezenta cerere de\nchemare în judecat&#259; în<a style='mso-footnote-id:ftn960' href=\"#_ftn960\"\nname=\"_ftnref960\" title=\"\"><sup><span style='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[960]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a><span\nstyle='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>.....<sup> </sup>exemplare.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> \n</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><span\nstyle='mso-spacerun:yes'>       </span>Anex&#259;m dovada achit&#259;rii taxei\njudiciare de timbru în cuantum de ..... lei &#351;i procura în original/copie\nlegalizat&#259;/împuternicirea avoca&#355;ial&#259;/extras, în copie\nlegalizat&#259;, din actul care atest&#259; dreptul de reprezentare<a\nstyle='mso-footnote-id:ftn961' href=\"#_ftn961\" name=\"_ftnref961\" title=\"\"><sup><span\nstyle='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[961]</span></sup><![endif]></span></sup></a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi-language:RO;mso-fareast-language:RO'>Data,<span style='mso-tab-count:\n10'>                                                                                       </span><span\nstyle='mso-spacerun:yes'>        </span>Semn&#259;tura<a style='mso-footnote-id:\nftn962' href=\"#_ftn962\" name=\"_ftnref962\" title=\"\"><sup><span style='mso-special-character:\nfootnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sup><span\nstyle='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nRO;mso-fareast-language:RO;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[962]</span></sup></b><![endif]></span></sup></a>,<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:\nnormal'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\nmso-ansi